import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import { Provider } from 'react-redux';
import { createStore, combineReducers } from 'redux';
import './index.css';
import * as serviceWorker from './serviceWorker';
import ActivityLog from './UserConsole/ActivityLog/ActivityLog';
import DocumentRepo from './UserConsole/DocumentRepo/DocumentRepo';
import { Route, Switch, BrowserRouter as Router } from 'react-router-dom';
import { routerReducer } from 'react-router-redux';
import UserUpload from './UserConsole/UserUpload/UserUpload';
import DocumentRepoAdmin from './AdminConsole/DocumentRepoAdmin/DocumentRepoAdmin'
import AccessControl from './AdminConsole/AccessControl/AccessControl';
import AdminUpload from './AdminConsole/AdminUpload/AdminUpload';
import AuditLog from './AdminConsole/AuditLog/AuditLog';
import EditDetails from './AdminConsole/EditDetails/EditDetails'
import Home from './Home/Home'
import {
    userActivityLogSearchData,
    userActivityLogSortData,
    documentRepoInfoData,
    userDocumentRepoSearchData,
    userDocumentRepoSortData,
    userDocumentRepoStatusData,
    adminAuditLogInfoData,
    adminAuditLogSortData,
    adminAuditLogSearchData,
    adminDocumentRepoSearchData,
    adminDocumentRepoSortData,
    adminDocumentRepoStatusData,
    adminAccessControlDeptFilterData,
    adminAccessControlSelectedRowsData,
    adminAccessControlInfoData,
    typeOptionsData,
    marketOptionsData,
    languageOptionsData,
    fileUploadCompleteData,
    fileUploadInProgress,
    fileSubmitCompleteData,
    userEditDocumentRepoStatusData,
    adminEditDocumentRepoStatusData,
    selectedRowUserDocRepoData,
    selectedRowAdminDocRepoData,
    userEditFieldData,
    userEditValueData,
    adminEditFieldData,
    adminEditValueData,
    userLogInData
} from './reducers';

const rootReducer = combineReducers({
    userActivityLogSearchData,
    userActivityLogSortData,
    documentRepoInfoData,
    userDocumentRepoSearchData,
    userDocumentRepoSortData,
    userDocumentRepoStatusData,
    adminAuditLogInfoData,
    adminAuditLogSortData,
    adminAuditLogSearchData,
    adminDocumentRepoSearchData,
    adminDocumentRepoSortData,
    adminDocumentRepoStatusData,
    adminAccessControlDeptFilterData,
    adminAccessControlSelectedRowsData,
    adminAccessControlInfoData,
    typeOptionsData,
    marketOptionsData,
    languageOptionsData,
    fileUploadCompleteData,
    fileUploadInProgress,
    fileSubmitCompleteData,
    userEditDocumentRepoStatusData,
    adminEditDocumentRepoStatusData,
    selectedRowUserDocRepoData,
    selectedRowAdminDocRepoData,
    userEditFieldData,
    userEditValueData,
    adminEditFieldData,
    adminEditValueData,
    userLogInData,
    router: routerReducer
})

const store = createStore(rootReducer, window.__REDUX_DEVTOOLS_EXTENSION__ && window.__REDUX_DEVTOOLS_EXTENSION__())

ReactDOM.render(<Provider store={store}>
    <Router>
        <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/" component={Home} />
            <Route
                path="/User"
                render={({ match: { url } }) => (
                    <>
                        <Route path={`${url}/DocumentRepo`} component={DocumentRepo} />
                        <Route path={`${url}/ActivityLog`} component={ActivityLog} />
                        <Route path={`${url}/UserUpload`} component={UserUpload} />
                    </>
                )}
            />
            <Route
                path="/Admin"
                render={({ match: { url } }) => (
                    <>
                        <Route path={`${url}/DocumentRepo`} component={DocumentRepoAdmin} />
                        <Route path={`${url}/AuditLog`} component={AuditLog} />
                        <Route path={`${url}/AdminUpload`} component={AdminUpload} />
                        <Route path={`${url}/AccessControl`} component={AccessControl} />
                        <Route path={`${url}/EditDetails`} component={EditDetails} />
                    </>
                )}
            />
        </Switch>
    </Router>
</Provider>, document.getElementById('root'));
serviceWorker.unregister();
